	The RichFaces Components


		The library encompasses ready-made components built based on 
		the Rich Faces CDK.
	
	


		
		Ajax Support

The component in this section lets you easily add  Ajax capabilities to other components as well as manage Ajax requests. 
		
		&a4j_ajaxListener;
		&a4j_actionparam;
		&a4j_form;
		&a4j_region;
		&a4j_support;
		&a4j_commandButton;
		&a4j_commandLink;
		&a4j_jsFunction;
		&a4j_poll;
		&a4j_push;
		&a4j_queue;
		&a4j_status;
	


		
		Resources/Beans Handling

The main purpose of the components covered in this section is to load resources (style sheets, JavaScript files and resource bundle) and to keep a state of a bean between requests. 
		
		
		&a4j_loadBundle;
		&a4j_keepAlive;
		&a4j_loadScript;
		&a4j_loadStyle;
	


		
		Ajax Validators

RichFaces components library provides 3 components to validate user input data. 
			These components enhance JSF validation capabilities with Ajax support and possibility to use Hibernate validators.   
		
		&rich_ajaxValidator;
		&rich_beanValidator;
		&rich_graphValidator;
	


		
		Ajax Output

The components described in this section render some content dynamically using Ajax capabilities.
		
		&a4j_include;
		&a4j_mediaOutput;
		&a4j_outputPanel;
	


		
		Ajax Miscellaneous

A collection of Ajax Miscellaneous components
		
		&a4j_page;
		&a4j_portlet;
		&a4j_htmlCommandLink;
		&a4j_log;
	


		
		Data Iteration
		

	The following components iterate over a collection of data and represent it on the page.
		
		&rich_column;
		&rich_columnGroup;
		&rich_columns;
		&rich_dataDefinitionList;
		&rich_dataFilterSlider;
		&rich_dataGrid;
		&rich_dataList;
		&rich_dataOrderedList;
		&rich_datascroller;
		&rich_dataTable;
		&rich_subTable;
		&rich_extendedDataTable;
		&a4j_repeat;
		&rich_scrollableDataTable;
	


		
		Drag-Drop Support


			In this section you will find components that help you build drag-and-drop controls, manage their behaviour and define the area on the page to be used as a drop zone. 
		
		
		&rich_dragIndicator;
		&rich_dragSupport;
		&rich_dragListener;
		&rich_dropListener;
		&rich_dropSupport;
		&rich_dndParam;
	


		
		Rich Menu
		


			This section tells how you  can create menus on your page: either navigational ones or context. 
		
		
		
		&rich_contextMenu;
		&rich_dropDownMenu;
		&rich_menuGroup;
		&rich_menuItem;
		&rich_menuSeparator;
	


		
		Rich Trees
			


				In this section you will learn how to build  hierarchical data presentation using the <rich:tree> component.
			
		
		&rich_tree;
		&rich_treeNode;
		&rich_treeNodesAdaptor;
		&rich_recursiveTreeNodesAdaptor;
		&rich_changeExpandListener;
		&rich_nodeSelectListener;
	


		
		Rich Output


				This section covers the components that are designed to be used as output and UI elements.
			
		
		&rich_modalPanel;
		&rich_paint2D;
		&rich_panel;
		&rich_panelBar;
		&rich_panelBarItem;
		&rich_panelMenu;
		&rich_panelMenuGroup;
		&rich_panelMenuItem;
		&rich_progressBar;
		&rich_separator;
		&rich_simpleTogglePanel;
		&rich_spacer;
		&rich_tabPanel;
		&rich_tab;
		&rich_togglePanel;
		&rich_toggleControl;
		&rich_toolBar;
		&rich_toolBarGroup;
		&rich_toolTip;
	


		
		Rich Input


			In this section you will find the components that help you deal with various kinds of user inputs from picking a date, WYSIWYG text editing to uploading a file.
		
		
		&rich_calendar;
		&rich_colorPicker;
		&rich_comboBox;
		&rich_editor;
		&rich_fileUpload;
		&rich_inplaceInput;
		&rich_inplaceSelect;
		&rich_inputNumberSlider;
		&rich_inputNumberSpinner;
		&rich_suggestionbox;
	


		
		Rich Selects


			RichFaces library provides desktop like complex controls to implement user select functionality. 
		
		
		&rich_listShuttle;
		&rich_orderingList;
		&rich_pickList;
	


		
		Rich Semantic Layouts


			Layout components enrich RichFaces with functionality that enables you to create the whole page layout and define the parameters of the page. 
			You can also create your custom theme and use it alongside with these components. 
		
		
		&rich_page;
		&rich_layout;
		&rich_layoutPanel;
	


		
		Rich Miscellaneous

A collection of Ajax Miscellaneous components
		
		&rich_componentControl;
		&rich_effect;
		&rich_gmap;
		&rich_virtualEarth;
		&rich_hotKey;
		&rich_insert;
		&rich_message;
		&rich_messages;
		&rich_jQuery;
		


